reviewText: This is an amazing course if you're into tinkering/makerspaces/STEAM! Tons of examples backed by strong educational practices.  I totally recommend it!
Excellent content and best practices for a teacher interested in STEM!

I loved this course!  Challenging yet supportive, inspiring and fresh.  The instructors seemed genuinely interested in my success.  This was my first Coursera course.... I hope the rest are as good as this.
The class was both fun and interesting.   Thanks so much!
